entries.title: Entry 1
entries.text: This is all new to me. I hope to keep a 'beginner's mind' about it all throughout it all. Hopefully, watching this journey will be illuminating to some. As I will explain in later posts, I do not intend this space to be grounds for dialogue - but if you wish to, I am more than willing in other formats. You can find my contact info here.
